  "3242830": {
    "name": "Ars Vox Arcana",
    "steam_appid": 3242830,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ars Vox Arcana</strong> 是一款以语音驱动的奇幻<strong>对决游戏</strong>，在游戏中你通过口头咒语指挥魔法。 <br>无论是在完全的虚拟现实中，还是在使用电脑、鼠标和键盘的情况下，你都扮演着一位用言语塑造现实的巫师。这不仅仅是施法，而是一种源于语言的魔法.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242830/extras/ed8e93e312e9d3f4326f6a27b35250be.avif?t=1746830772\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242830/extras_big/ed8e93e312e9d3f4326f6a27b35250be.avif?t=1746830772 width=800 height=208 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与朋友们展开魔法对决，策略和施法技巧决定胜负.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242830/extras/afe5ec21a5cca5de39a20460fbf3c646.avif?t=1746830772\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242830/extras_big/afe5ec21a5cca5de39a20460fbf3c646.avif?t=1746830772 width=800 height=208 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >说出咒语，塑造世界。使用模块化的神秘短语实时构建咒语。每个单词都会改变结果——没有菜单，只有魔法.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242830/extras/ed6682e699456848b317055e9a3b6868.avif?t=1746830772\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242830/extras_big/ed6682e699456848b317055e9a3b6868.avif?t=1746830772 width=800 height=208 /></span>Ars Vox Arcana 旨在提供沉浸式虚拟现实体验，同时也完美支持传统PC游戏.<br>两种模式都提供相同的深度、魔法艺术和进程.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242830/extras/148f74413d432bfa8046ea41b6d44aa3.avif?t=1746830772\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242830/extras_big/148f74413d432bfa8046ea41b6d44aa3.avif?t=1746830772 width=800 height=208 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >融合隐藏的形态、元素和力量的低语。探索全新的互动，磨练你的仪式之声，并尝试神秘的结构.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242830/extras/0c17900feb9eda4ef194439e980f40f6.avif?t=1746830772\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242830/extras_big/0c17900feb9eda4ef194439e980f40f6.avif?t=1746830772 width=800 height=208 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >所有操作均在本地处理，实现无缝且私密的施法体验。无云端，无延迟——你的声音立即生效.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242830/extras/9933994a3d82dbbc2bf37fb890c3045b.avif?t=1746830772\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242830/extras_big/9933994a3d82dbbc2bf37fb890c3045b.avif?t=1746830772 width=800 height=208 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解锁语言的更深层次。寻找被遗忘语句的碎片，每一部分都是更伟大魔法真理的一环.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语<strong>*</strong>, 德语<strong>*</strong>, 西班牙语 - 西班牙<strong>*</strong>, 俄语<strong>*</strong>, 简体中文<strong>*</strong>, 乌克兰语<strong>*</strong><br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
